title: Ella Beatty and Hugh Jackman Live in NYC
description: Don't miss Ella Beatty, Hugh Jackman, Liev Schreiber, Maggie Siff, and Justice Smith in two plays at Audible's Minetta Lane Theatre, directed in rep by Ian Rickson through June 18 only. The plays include 'Sexual Misconduct of the Middle Classes' and 'Creditors'.
cost: $35 at the box office, $86.50 advance tickets
